<div id="review_403188542" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/403188542" />
    <a title="Kathleen" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/12024746-kathleen"><img alt="Kathleen" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1613522159p2/12024746.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/403188542?book_show_action=true">Aug 29, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kathleen" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kathleen" href="/user/show/12024746-kathleen">Kathleen</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12024746-kathleen?shelf=christianity">christianity</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer403188542" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8134953352435975106">This little book is so incredibly helpful when the rivers of prayer run dry ....which in my case so often do. This inspiring book doesn&apos;t merely touch the heart, it scrapes it out, revealing the evil motives that lurk within, shining the light on our perpetual inconsistencies. Valley of Vision is just that, it speaks to you in the valley &amp; most certainly gives clarity to your spiritual vision. There&apos;s a good reason this book is still around &amp; will be for a long time to come!</span>
  <span id="freeText8134953352435975106" style="display:none">This little book is so incredibly helpful when the rivers of prayer run dry ....which in my case so often do. This inspiring book doesn't merely touch the heart, it scrapes it out, revealing the evil motives that lurk within, shining the light on our perpetual inconsistencies. Valley of Vision is just that, it speaks to you in the valley &amp; most certainly gives clarity to your spiritual vision. There's a good reason this book is still around &amp; will be for a long time to come!</span>
  <a data-text-id="8134953352435975106" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


