  <span id="freeText13261094197131508403" style="display:none">A wonderful collection of prayers that I will without a doubt return to again and again. Walking through this book has been a profound help in strengthening my own personal prayer life. What Arthur Bennett has done in compiling these prayers and devotions has had a impact greater than he himself ever could have imagined. Each prayer is steeped in Scripture, filled with sound doctrine and, most importantly, points to Christ. The Puritans' writings have had an impact on my Christian life greater than anything else outside of the Bible, and these prayers and devotions are no exception. Read them - slowly, prayerfully, allowing them to encourage and challenge you. It's worth your time and effort! </span>
