<div id="review_2877025451" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2877025451" />
    <a title="Courtney | Lasting Joy Reads" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3799997-courtney-lasting-joy-reads"><img alt="Courtney | Lasting Joy Reads" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1644104792p2/3799997.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2877025451?book_show_action=true">Dec 11, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Courtney | Lasting Joy Reads" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Courtney | Lasting Joy Reads" href="/user/show/3799997-courtney-lasting-joy-reads">Courtney | Lasting Joy Reads</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3799997-courtney-lasting-joy-reads?shelf=2020-book-challenge">2020-book-challenge</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2877025451" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6909933367598213208">What a treasure this book is. This book is a collection of Puritan prayers from authors in the 17th, 18th, and 19th century. The prayers were so rich and theologically sound. I read this in the mornings after I read the Bible. One of my prayers is to have a richer prayer life. These are a great template to emulate. I highly recommend this book. I’d love to get the leather bound version someday. I’ll definitely incorporate this book in 2021 as well!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

